      </div>
      <div class="p-home__recruitTextArea">
        <h2 class="c-sectionTitle">
          <strong class="c-sectionTitle__main">RECRUIT</strong>
          <span class="c-sectionTitle__caption">採用情報</span>
        </h2>
        <p>私たちと一緒に働きませんか？</p>
        <div class="c-btn">
          <a href="/contact">
